 a moment to answer our <a href=\'https://events.wordpress.test/rome/2023/training/?page_id=6\'>post-event survey</a> and help us to do amazing WordPress events!\r\n(If you can\'t open the link, copy and paste the following URL)\r\nhttps://events.wordpress.test/rome/2023/training/?page_id=6\r\n\r\nPlease complete the survey by 2024-01-05.\r\n\r\nPlease also note that all responses will be kept confidential, and we will not share your personal information with any third parties.\r\n\r\nThank you in advance, we really appreciate your time!\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\nOrganising Team,\r\nRome 2023 Training','[first_name], tell us what you thought: Post-event survey','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2023-12-22 16:29:30','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://events.wordpress.test/rome/2023/training/?post_type=tix_email&p=7',0,'tix_email','',0),(8,1,'2023-12-22 17:44:44','0000-00-00 00:00:00','Howdy [email],\r\n\r\nCongratulations on completing Rome Community Day 2023! We hope you had a great time, and that you\'ll soon get some well-deserved rest\r\n\r\nWe\'d love to hear how you feel the event went. What were your proudest moments and your greatest disappointments?\r\nWe\'ve created an Organizer Survey, so we can get all the details of how things went with your event. <strong>Please fill it out this form within 10 days:</strong> https://central.wordcamp.test/organizer-survey-event-debrief/?t=9043c11708cbcc4299ad9ce65d7f8a3578d90525888a659bf9d0b9ba3d6107b2&#038;wid=48\r\n\r\n<strong>Event Budget</strong>\r\nPlease update your working budget on your event dashboard. If you ran your money outside of WordPress Community Support, PBC, please also balance your budget spreadsheet and prepare your Transparency Report.If there are any issues, please reach out to us at support@wordcamp.org to schedule a budget close-out meeting. Please complete these steps within the next two weeks.\r\n\r\n<strong>Event Recording (if any)</strong>\r\nIf you haven\'t yet done so, please review the submission guidelines before beginning to edit your videos (or before your videographers starts editing): http://blog.wordpress.tv/submission-guidelines/\r\n\r\nTo submit your video for publication to WordPress.tv, just upload them at this page: http://wordpress.tv/submit-video/\r\n\r\nOur intrepid team of video moderators will review the videos and schedule them for publication. If your content is in a language other than English, please see if you can recruit someone from your community to join the WordPress TV moderators\' team and review your videos: http://wordpress.tv/apply-to-be-a-wordpress-tv-moderator/\r\n\r\n<strong>Event Recap</strong>\r\nFinally, if you\'ve published a recap on your site, please let us know, so we can reblog it on the WordCamp Central blog.\r\n\r\nThanks again for all you\'ve done to grow the WordPress community in Rome!\r\n\r\nBest wishes,\r\nYour friendly WordCamp Central crew','Organizer Survey (event debrief)','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2023-12-22 17:44:44','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://events.wordpress.test/rome/2023/training/?p=8',0,'tix_email','',0),(9,1,'2023-12-22 17:44:44','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','widget_image','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2023-12-22 17:44:44','0000-00-00 00:00:00','a:1:{s:12:\"_multiwidget\";i:1;}',0,'https://events.wordpress.test/rome/2023/training/?post_type=jetpack_migration&p=9',0,'jetpack_migration','',0),(10,1,'2023-12-22 17:44:44','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','sidebars_widgets','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2023-12-22 17:44:44','0000-00-00 00:00:00','a:3:{s:19:\"wp_inactive_widgets\";a:0:{}s:9:\"sidebar-1\";a:3:{i:0;s:7:\"block-2\";i:1;s:7:\"block-3\";i:2;s:7:\"block-4\";}s:9:\"sidebar-2\";a:2:{i:0;s:7:\"block-5\";i:1;s:7:\"block-6\";}}',0,'https://events.wordpress.test/rome/2023/training/?post_type=jetpack_migration&p=10',0,'jetpack_migration','',0);
