e is welcome to come share & grow in their skills!',5,'Inland Empire WordPress Meetup Group','https://www.meetup.com/inlandempirewp/','2024-01-09 19:00:00','-28800','2024-01-09 21:00:00','online','US',33.99,-117.37),(73348987,'meetup','292287659','scheduled','VIRTUAL WordPress Developer Night - #IEWP','https://www.meetup.com/inlandempirewp/events/292287659','The Inland Empire Dev Meetup is intended for intermediate to advanced developers. At this meetup we talk about WordPress-relevant-code-level things.\n\nTechnologies:\n- PHP & Javascript\n- HTML5 / CSS\n- Javascript Frameworks\n- Modern Web Development Workflows\n\nWe are web developers first, then WordPress developers. We have an [in progress] skills ladder that gets updated regularly.\n\nSKILLS LADDER: https://github.com/Inland-Empire-WordPress-Meetup/\n\nWe also welcome any developer presentations that are relevant to developing websites for WordPress. We look for unique workflows. Submit your talks below:\n\nSUBMIT TALK: https://inlandempirewp.com/speaker-request/\n\nEveryone is welcome to come share & grow in their skills!',3,'Inland Empire WordPress Meetup Group','https://www.meetup.com/inlandempirewp/','2024-01-09 19:00:00','-28800','2024-01-09 21:00:00','online','US',33.99,-117.37),(73348988,'meetup','298060486','scheduled','WordPress Meetup','https://www.meetup.com/wp-fayetteville/events/298060486','Join us Tuesday the 8th from 6:00-8:00pm. We\'ll be planning out our Meetup Group\'s topics for the next year. If you would like to suggest any ideas, volunteer to lead a discussion, or just want to brainstorm with everybody, come on out!',1,'WordPress Fayetteville Meetup Group','https://www.meetup.com/WP-Fayetteville/','2024-01-09 18:00:00','-21600','2024-01-09 19:45:00','Springdale, AR, USA','us',36.18391,-94.13918),(73348989,'meetup','297931955','scheduled','WordPress Happiness Hour','https://www.meetup.com/denverwordpress/events/297931955','If you are a front-end designer, intense developer, writer, or a person that likes to poke around on the Dashboard, then come on by. Bring your WordPress work and questions.\n\nThis meetup is held virtually via Discord. Please RSVP for the link.',3,'Denver WordPress Meetup','https://www.meetup.com/DenverWordPress/','2024-01-09 18:00:00','-25200','2024-01-09 20:00:00','online','US',39.77,-105.01),(73348990,'meetup','292286301','scheduled','ONLINE DISCUSSION- Learn about your DIVI Theme- Divisociety.com','https://www.meetup.com/milwaukee-wordpress-meetup/events/292286301','A FREE WordPress meetup for beginner to intermediate users, who get together to share our knowledge and experience, and to meet other local fans and aficionados of WordPress.\n\nWe will be covering anything and everything about what we consider the easiest and best WordPress website/page designer or builder. Going over how to use the tool as well as showing some easy and powerful tips. We think once you have experienced Divi â€“ youâ€™ll love it as much as we do!\n\nThe Milwaukee WordPress Meetup for DIVI THEME is for individuals, entrepreneurs and small business owners wanting to learn what, why and how WordPress DIVI THEME is a powerful content publishing platform, marketing tool, social media hub, CMS and complete website solution. This WordPress Meetup is open to all who are interested in or love WordPress --- join us!\n\nThere is absolutely no agenda! Come with your questions, issues, or concerns. This will be an open conversation every month, so that we are able to help one another with answers, suggestions, our favorite tools or plugins, etc.\n\nWe are using Zoom for these Online events.\n\nRegister in advance for this meeting:\nhttps://zoom.us/meeting/register/tJUvf-qtrzgoPTvl1FPZIDWWNVSQe6EDlQ\n\nAfter registering, you will receive a confirmation email containing information about joining the meeting.\n\nThis event is occurring every other week.',6,'Greater Milwaukee Area WordPress Meetup','https://www.meetup.com/Milwaukee-WordPress-MeetUp/','2024-01-09 18:00:00','-21600','2024-01-09 19:30:00','online','US',43.04,-87.92),(73348991,'meetup','298049561','scheduled','Online: WordPress Help Desk','https://www.meetup.com/raleigh-wordpress-meetup-group/events/298049561','â†“â†“â†“â†“â†“â†“â†“â†“â†“â†“ Please read the description. â†“â†“â†“â†“â†“â†“â†“â†“â†“â†“\n\nGo here to schedule a call: [https://optsus.com/wp-help-desk/](https://optsus.com/wp-help-desk/)\n\nAs the pandemic wanes, there is a \"new normal\" for the WordPress Help Desk.\n\nWordPress Help Desk events will be online as a 1-on-1 WordPress Help Desk call.\n\nTo schedule a 1-on-1 WordPress Help Desk call, simply use the calendar found here: [https://optsus.com/wp-help-desk/](https://optsus.com/wp-help-desk/)\n\nConfused? Please read this entire description including the TLDR and FAQ sections to clear up any confusion about changes as this event has changed from in-person to online.\n\nWe look forward to helping you with WordPress.\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-TLDR\\-\\-\\-\\-\n\nI\'m adding to the description because some people have been confused by these events. The link above is for you to schedule the WordPress Help Desk 1-on-1 call. The available times are generally from 9 AM until 10 AM, which is why this event is scheduled for that time. However, this is not a group call.\n\nWhen the world shifted to hosting events from home, back in March of 2020, I tested this as a group call. As people received answers for their questions about WordPress, they left the call. This frustrated the people who had to wait and listen to the other questions and answers during the call. I don\'t want to waste everyone\'s time in this way.\n\nAt an in-person event, it\'s possible to work in a group and ask questions as they come up. However, this does not transition into a video conference call very well. Instead, I have opened up my calendar to schedule 1-on-1 calls using the link above. We will focus on the one question you have about your website.\n\nThe reason this event is reoccurring here on Meetup is to let you know the WordPress Help Desk events are still available. Before the pandemic, this was an event hosted in Raleigh once per month for two hours. Now, this is a 1-on-1 video conference call scheduled for 20 minute blocks multiple times throughout the month.\n\nThere will be no link shared for a group call with this event. The WordPress Help Desk events have become 1-on-1 video conference calls which can be scheduled using the link above.\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-FAQ\\-\\-\\-\\-\n\nWhere is the link to join the call?\n\n* If you are looking for a link to join a group call, there isn\'t one. These events have moved to 1-on-1 scheduled appointments. When you schedule your appointment, you will receive a confirmation email with a link to join your 1-on-1 call.\n\nWhy can\'t I get into the Zoom call?\n\n* Please check the date and time in the confirmation email for your scheduled 1-on-1 call, after using the link above to schedule your 1-on-1 WordPress Help Desk call.\n* Also, we use Google Meet for these calls. It\'s similar to Zoom, just a different brand of video calling.\n\nWhy is this event repeating each morning, but there are no available appointment times this morning?\n\n* These calls are scheduled in advance. If there is no time available today, you can book your call for the next available time.\n\nWhat is the point of having these events on Meetup if we are scheduling 1-on-1 calls with another calendar?\n\n* These events were held in-person with 20 - 50 people attending once per month. Since the pandemic forced these events to move online, we have helped more people than we did in the past with in-person events. For this reason, the WordPress Help Desk events will remain online using scheduled 1-on-1 calls. Use the link above to schedule your call for a convenient time.',1,'Raleigh-Durham RTP WordPress Meetup Group','https://www.meetup.com/Raleigh-WordPress-Meetup-Group/','2024-01-09 09:00:00','-18000','2024-01-09 10:00:00','online','US',35.89,-78.64),(73348992,'meetup','297374467','scheduled','WordPress Payments, Renewals, Donations Zoom WordPress Cambridge Mon Jan 8th 7pm','https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-cambridge/events/297374467','Monday Jan 8th on Zoom, 7pm we will explore/discuss taking payments, e.g. PayPal, Stripe etc, renewal subscriptions, donations, fees on a WordPress site.\n\nApols, don\'t yet have a zoom link, but that will appear shortly. The link for the meeting is [https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-cambridge/events/297374467/](https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-cambridge/events/297374467/)\n\nMainly, this is discussion/sharing group, rather than a single speaker/you listen group. Everyone is invited to share their knowledge, expertise, tips, & tricks. On Zoom, you\'re welcome to share your screen to show how you achieved something.\n\nPlus, anyone can ask a question or seek some quick advice. Beginner questions are great, as well as questions from people who know the topic. We hope everyone else learns something, and leaves people thinking \"i could do that\".\n\nWe have a wonderful crowd on Zoom, from across the USA, UK, Ireland, and Europe. Alas, we don\'t have enough people close to Cambridge to justify actually meeting in town. So the meetup is only on Zoom.\n\nThanks to Chris Cox of https://www.hihub.info/ for providing Zoom. I\'ll send out a recording of the meeting afterwards.\n\nThis format seems to work.\n\n7pm: Welcome. Depending on numbers, everyone gets to introduce themselves, perhaps 10 seconds each, mainly describing their involvement with WordPress. If we have many attendees, then introductions via the chat.\n\n7:15 pm: Start of sharing & discussion.\n\n8.30pm The meeting kinda starts to wind up, sometimes we chat for longer. Then we decide next month\'s topic.\n\n9:00pm We aim to finish.\n\nLooking forward to seeing and chatting with everyone.\n\nSimon & Chris',22,'WordPress Cambridge Meetup','https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-cambridge/','2024-01-08 19:00:00','0','2024-01-08 21:00:00','online','GB',52.21,0.13),(73348993,'meetup','297520179','scheduled','2024 Welcome Meetup','https://www.meetup.com/port-au-prince-wordpress-meetup/events/297520179','C\'est le premier rendez-vous de notre Chapitre pour l\'annÃ©e 2024!\n\nCette session est destinÃ©e Ã  vous aider Ã  rencontrer d\'autres futurs utilisateurs, et codeurs de notre groupe et Ã  parler de notre expÃ©rience de WordPress.\n\nVenez rencontrer d\'autres utilisateurs de WordPress, discuter de nos intÃ©rÃªts, l\'objectif du Group WordPress Meetup et le plan pour l\'annee 2024!\n\nNous vous encourageons a consulter les liens ci-dessous avant de participer:\nhttps://make.wordpress.org/community/meetups/\n\nCe meetup est destinÃ©e Ã  tous les niveaux de compÃ©tences. Si vous Ãªtes un utilisateur expÃ©rimentÃ©, prÃ©parez-vous Ã  offrir votre aide. Pour les nouveaux WordPressers, laissez-nous vous donner un coup de main! Et comme toujours, veuillez RSVP.\n\nCode de conduite meetup en ligne\nhttps://make.wordpress.org/community/handbook/virtual-events/online-code-of-conduct/\n\nRejoignez nous egalement sur les reseaux sociaux:\n\n* Facebook page https://web.facebook.com/papwordpressmeetup\n* Linkedin https://linkedin.com/groups/12445027\n* Facebook group https://web.facebook.com/groups/papwordpressmeetup\n* Instagram https://www.instagram.com/papwpmeetup/\n* Twitter https://twitter.com/papwpmeetup\n* Telegram https://t.me/joinchat/ILPdGq1Spa8dx6I4',7,'Port-au-Prince WordPress Meetup Group','https://www.meetup.com/Port-au-Prince-WordPress-Meetup/','2024-01-06 14:00:00','-18000','2024-01-06 16:00:00','online','HT',18.54,-72.34),(73348994,'meetup','297831532','scheduled','WordPress Roundtable','https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-midcities-user-group/events/297831532','Our WordPress MeetUp community is mostly comprised of beginners and DIY\'ers. We try to cover topics that will benefit beginner and intermediate users. We mostly function as a roundtable, where all community members can cont